                <h2>For Recruiters</h2>
        <p>Welcome to the Placement Cell. We are dedicated to connecting top talent with leading companies. Here’s how we can assist you:</p>

        <h3>Our Services for Recruiters</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>On-campus Recruitment Drives:</strong> We organize recruitment drives where you can meet and interview potential candidates directly on our campus.</li>
            <li><strong>Job Fairs:</strong> Participate in our job fairs to engage with a large pool of students and recent graduates.</li>
            <li><strong>Internship Programs:</strong> Access our database of students looking for internship opportunities to find the right match for your organization.</li>
            <li><strong>Custom Recruitment Solutions:</strong> We provide tailored recruitment solutions to meet your specific hiring needs.</li>
            <li><strong>Brand Promotion:</strong> Enhance your company’s visibility on campus through sponsorship and collaboration in various events.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Register Your Interest</h3>
        <p>If you are interested in recruiting our students, please fill out the form below, and we will get in touch with you:</p>

        <form action="/recruiters" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="companyName">Company Name:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="companyName" name="companyName" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contactPerson">Contact Person:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="contactPerson" name="contactPerson" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="phone">Phone Number:</label>
                <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phone" name="phone" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="jobPositions">Job Positions Available:</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" id="jobPositions" name="jobPositions" rows="3" required></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">Submit</button>
        </form>
